item.title: CVE-2016-9716|2024-09-17T02:52:02.444Z -- ibm -- infosphere%20master%20data%20management
item.description: IBM InfoSphere Master Data Management Server 11.0, 11.3, 11.4, 11.5, and 11.6 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 119729.
